    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a solid project or budget-friendly driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains smoke-free. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a reliable enough car for daily use, provided you're comfortable with its cosmetic imperfections and upcoming maintenance needs.",
