      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this expertly maintained vehicle, representing a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This selection has undergone a rigorous assessment to ensure mechanical reliability and aesthetic preservation. Featuring a documented history of consistent care, it offers a refined driving experience and remains a steadfast example of its class. This is an exceptional opportunity for the professional buyer seeking a high-caliber vehicle with a proven service record.",
      "price": 34800.0,
